    Methods called by generated attributes to perform common type conversions.

    Attributes will uniformly call GeneratedAttributeSupport.valueOf(), and during compilation the compiler will take care of compiling the attribute to call the most specific valueOf() method for the type of the value read by the attribute automatically.
